FF-LocalKnowledgeBase
Copyright 2026 FF-LocalKnowledgeBase contributors

This project implements an original, agent-neutral local knowledge workflow.
Its design was informed by the public Agent Skills specification and by common
test-first, verification, and code-review practices in the AI coding ecosystem.

No private project pages, customer data, production schemas, internal logs, or
workspace-specific knowledge are included in this distribution.

The `agents/openai.yaml` files are optional OpenAI/Codex adapter metadata. The
canonical skills remain portable `SKILL.md` packages and do not require OpenAI
services.
